responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "332011524CF41D34998B838238711D4C", "There\'s no doubt he\'s a Kaelar an\' all, but not all of us have the wherewithal to make a stand against the goblin rampage. It\'s been only getting worse of late, and we villagers lack the gumption to hold our shields against their attacks. We\'re worn down here, and it wouldn\'t be a surprise to me if he abandoned his support for us once he\'s realized it\'s an uphill battle.")
